-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discovery Client
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- all applications that register on the discovery server

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
discovery aware @SpringBootApplication
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
include a Spring Discovery Client (Eureka, Zookeeper, etc.)
- spring-cloud-netflix-eureka-client
- spring-cloud-starter-netflix-eureka-client
- spring-cloud-starter-zookeeper-discovery

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- @EnableDiscoveryClient / @EnableEurekaClient
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- annotate a @Configuration with either  @EnableDiscoveryClient or
  @EnableEurekaClient
- optional with spring-cloud-starter-netflix-eureka-client
- with Zookeeper: @EnableDiscoveryClient

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Random Port
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
We can let Spring Boot choose a random port for us because later we are
accessing this service with its name.
- server.port: 0